  "text": "These measurements were made with a pulse amplitude modulated fluorescence measuring system (H. Walz, Effeltrich, FRG) [CITATION_1] . The protocol for determining Fv/Fm values was described previously [CITATION_2] . For the DCMU-induced fluorescence induction experiment, two leaf discs were cut from a single leaf and floated upside down on 25°C water. One disc was exposed to low PFD (100 ,umol m-2 s-') and the other to high PFD ",
